description: The EU aims to enforce a UN arms embargo but remains concerned about migrant boats from Libya.
title: Libya conflict: EU agrees new patrols to stop arms flow
title_page: Libya conflict: EU agrees new patrols to stop arms flow - BBC News
maintext: Many of those rescued off Libya are refugees from the wars in Syria, Iraq and Afghanistan. But many impoverished migrants from sub-Saharan Africa also risk their lives on unseaworthy boats, desperate to flee the violence and abuse that are rife in Libya.
